               <title>WARNINGS AND PRECAUTIONS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>THIS MATERIAL WAS FILLED IN ACCORDANCE WITH OUR STANDARD OPERATING PROCEDURES UTILIZED FOR THE MANUFACTURE OF MEDICAL GASES.  THESE PROCEDURES ENSURE THAT PRODUCTS ARE SAFELY MANUFACTURED IN COMPLIANCE WITH THE FDA'S CURRENT GOOD MANUFACTURING PRACTICES (cGMP) REGULATIONS AND FDA MEDICAL GAS GUIDELINES FOR MEDICAL GAS CUSTOMERS.  FOR NON-MEDICAL CUSTOMERS, THIS MATERIAL IS NOT APPROVED FOR HUMAN DRUG USE.<br/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
